# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Cinematic Trader environment template
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Copy to `.env.local` for local development (already gitignored).
#
# SECURITY POLICY:
#   * NEVER prefix a private/server-only secret with `NEXT_PUBLIC_`. Anything
#     prefixed with `NEXT_PUBLIC_` is bundled into the JS sent to the browser.
#   * Provider API keys (email, AI providers, Stripe, etc.) MUST live on the
#     server only, used inside `app/api/**` route handlers, server actions,
#     or `lib/server/**`.
#   * If a secret is ever committed or leaked, ROTATE it immediately at the
#     provider, then update the deployment env (Vercel / hosting dashboard).
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# This project currently has NO required secrets — the only API hits public
# market data endpoints. Add server-only keys below if you wire up new
# providers (e.g. AI, email, payments).

# Examples (uncomment and fill when needed; never with NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix):
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# RESEND_API_KEY=
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=
# DATABASE_URL=
